## ✅ 7. Test `rewrite` behavior (if you use it)

```ts
proxy: {
  '/api': {
    target: env.VITE_API_GATEWAY_URL,
    changeOrigin: true,
    rewrite: path => path.replace(/^\/api/, '')
  }
