## ✅ 8. Common problems & how to detect them

### ❌ Proxy not triggering

**Symptom:** Backend never gets request  
**Fix:** Ensure request starts with `/api`

***

### ❌ Using full backend URL in code

```ts
❌ fetch('https://kmbld2c-optimus-uat.mykotaklife.com/api/...')
```

✅ Must use:

```ts
✅ fetch('/api/...')
```

***

### ❌ Environment variable not loaded

Check in config:

```ts
console.log(env.VITE_API_GATEWAY_URL);
```

Restart dev server after `.env` changes ✅

***

## ✅ 9. Golden checklist ✅

Before saying “proxy works”, confirm:

✔ Request URL starts with `/api`  
✔ Browser shows `localhost`  
✔ Vite logs show forwarding  
✔ Backend returns expected response  
✔ No CORS errors

